text: Manprit Sarkaria (born 26 August 1996) is an Austrian footballer who plays for Austria Wien as a left winger. ==Personal life== Born in Austria, Sarkaria is of Indian descent. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian footballers Category:Austrian people of Indian descent Category:Association football midfielders Category:FK Austria Wien players Category:Austrian Football Bundesliga players
